title: Oglaf (NSFW Web Comic) - Complete through 2014 {WebComixFan}
description:
"OGLAF" Web Comic

"Oglaf" (oglaf.com) by Trudy Cooper and Doug Bayne is an often seriously NSFW weekly Web comic.  In the words of its creators, it "started as an attempt to make pornography... [but] degenerated into sex comedy pretty much immediately."  Most of the episodes (called "stories") are single non-sequential pages, though some stretch out longer; the very first one was eight pages long.  The comic started out as a gag-a-week work, but slowly started including longer story arcs, which appear to be (very) slowly coming together into a single overarching plot.

This torrent includes "Oglaf" comic strips from its beginning in 2006 through the end of 2014 in a collection of CBR files, one for each year.  Each strip's page includes its title and both its regular and its "hidden" mouseover text comments
